#Text=Oh , thank you very much , everybody .
#Text=Thank you .
#Text=Well , thank you very much .
#Text=Thank you very much .
#Text=And considering that we caught President Obama and sleepy Joe Biden , spying on our campaign , treason , will probably be entitled to another four more years after that .
#Text=I wanted to thank you , and Art and Brandon , you 're incredible .
#Text=I 've known you now a long time .
#Text=Right from the beginning , we had the chemistry , we had that good chemistry …
#Text=Oh , sit down .
#Text=It 's 122 degrees in this place .
#Text=And we have our great Governor .
#Text=Governor , can we make it a little bit , just a little .
#Text=This is like a test .
#Text=You think Joe Biden could do this ?
#Text=I do n't think so .
#Text=So I 'm thrilled to be in Yuma , Arizona To proudly accept the endorsement of the National Border Patrol Council , that 's a big deal .
#Text=And they are great friends of mine .
#Text=And we 're building the wall .
#Text=Next week , we 'll be up to 300 miles of incredible wall .
#Text=And our numbers are the best .
#Text=We are very tough at the border .
#Text=When people want to come in , for our farmers , et cetera , et cetera , we 're not going to hurt our farmers , but we 've never had better numbers than we have right now .
#Text=And that 's been helped because we 're at a little bit over 280 miles right now , we have never been helped like this .

#Text=Wall , there are two things , in a thousand years you can come back , two things will never , with technology it 's obsolete before you even put it in the box , but two things never get old wheels and walls .
#Text=Wheels and wall .
#Text=If you come back in a thousand years , you 'll say , " Well , we still have wheels in walls . "
#Text=And that 's the only thing you 'll recognize .
#Text=The National Border Patrol Council is the official union representing the incredible heroes of the United States Border Patrol .
#Text=They 've been my friends from the beginning .

#Text=To every border agent , and I just met some unbelievable people backstage , these are great people , and every family member here today , you have earned the everlasting gratitude of our nation .
#Text=And I want to thank you very much .
#Text=Thank you very much .
#Text=As you know , better than anyone , the survival of our nation is at stake in this election .
#Text=And I will tell you , I never thought I 'd say it because we had a great election .
#Text=We had a great election a little while ago .
#Text=Four years ago , I never thought I 'd say anything could compete with 2016 .
#Text=This election that we 're going into is the most important election in the history of our country , because we had crooked Hillary , but this is something , these people are sick .
#Text=And we have to make sure that this radical left socialist and beyond , because this is beyond socialism , that it does n't happen , or we will indeed have Venezuela on steroids .
#Text=So we ca n't do it .
#Text=Most important election , November 3rd , get out and vote .
#Text=Joe Biden is the puppet of the radical left wing movement that seeks the complete elimination of America 's borders and boundaries .
#Text=They want to take the wall down , they do n't want to have borders , they want to have sanctuary cities , lots of bad things they want .
#Text=Following orders from his boss .
#Text=I guess his new boss is Bernie Sanders .
#Text=Can you believe that ?
#Text=Crazy Bernie .
#Text=Joe Biden has pledged to abolish immigration enforcement , suspend all removals , provide free government healthcare , and they want to give it to illegal aliens .
#Text=You do n't get it .
#Text=Restore , catching and release .
#Text=Shield violent criminal aliens .
#Text=This is what they want to do .
#Text=And give every illegal alien on the planet earth a free ticket to invent an asylum claim , and gain automatic admission into our country .
#Text=We will have people coming into our country that never even thought of it before .
#Text=You get free education , you get free healthcare , why would n't they come ?
#Text=Let 's go to America .
#Text=The Biden plan would unleash a flood of illegal immigration like the world has never seen .
#Text=It 's crazy .
#Text=Biden 's plan is the most radical , extreme , reckless , dangerous , and deadly immigration plan ever put forward by a major party candidate .
#Text=It must be defeated , and it will be defeated on November 3rd .
#Text=It will be defeated .
#Text=At last night 's Democrat convention , which by the way , got very bad ratings , I have to tell you .
#Text=Unity .
#Text=They talk about unity .
#Text=They want to bring unity .
#Text=And then you listen to Michelle Obama 's speech , which was obsolete by the time it got there .
#Text=She taped it .
#Text=No , she taped the speech .
#Text=It was obsolete .
#Text=She must have taped it about three weeks before .
#Text=I 'm speaking next Thursday , maybe I 'll tape it .
#Text=But I do n't think that goes .
#Text=That 's so much nicer , to tape it , you do it , nice air conditioned room .
#Text=And she not only taped it , but tell me when you hear a divisive speech …
#Text=They talk about me as being a divider .
#Text=I 'm not a divider .
#Text=I bring people together .
#Text=We were bringing people together .
#Text=We were bringing people together , like never before .
#Text=Success was bringing everyone together , and then we got hit with the China virus , but we were bringing people together .
#Text=But one of the opening speakers last night said that America will go to hell if we do n't have open borders .
#Text=Think of that .
#Text=Go to hell .
#Text=When a country does n't have borders , you do n't have a country .
#Text=Today , a Democrat speaker at the convention said , " We 're talking about abolishing the police , we 're talking about abolishing ICE , we 're talking about abolishing prisons . "
#Text=Biden 's campaign has turned into a cult for open border and others Zealots .

#Text=By the way , they want to double and triple your taxes , they want to increase regulations , they want to spend very little money on our vets , after we took care of our vets better than anyone 's .
#Text=91 % approval rate .
#Text=And they want to spend much less on our military , we 've totally rebuilt .
#Text=Two and a half trillion dollars , we 've totally rebuilt our military .
#Text=Bernie Sanders declared , in his speech , many of the ideas that just a few years ago were considered radical , are now mainstream .
#Text=That 's Bernie Sanders .
#Text=Because Joe , he does n't know where he is .
#Text=But if he did , he 's been brought so far left that our country will not be the country that we know .
#Text=It will have problems , it will go down .
#Text=Your stocks will be gone , your 401 ks will disappear .
#Text=And right now , who has the 401 k ?
#Text=And then the rest of you , many of you have stocks , and you do it a different way .
#Text=That will go down 50 , 60 , 70 % , 80 % .
#Text=And if you held on , like I said to do , we went down a little while we got hit with a virus .
#Text=Now , NASDAQ just broke an all time record .
#Text=SNP , just broke an all time record .
#Text=Socialism is the mainstream of the Biden campaign and it 's not the mainstream of America .
#Text=Remember I said , we will never have a socialist country .
#Text=On November 3rd .
#Text=The people of Arizona , our great state , we love Arizona .
#Text=I won it last time , by a lot .
#Text=And I hear we 're going to win it by even more this time .
#Text=Do n't forget , last time I talked , I said we 're going to give you a tax cuts , I gave you .
#Text=I said , we 're going to give you a massive regulation cuts .
#Text=Give you your tax cuts , I gave them to you .
#Text=I said we 're going to give you massive regulation cuts , we 're going to give you great everything .
#Text=We even did Right to Try medicine .
#Text=You know all about that .
#Text=We did things that I did n't even talk about it , we did .
#Text=We did a thing called the Space Force .
#Text=You never heard me talking about .
#Text=I 'm the only candidate that gave you more than I promised in the campaign .
#Text=It 's true .
#Text=I 'm the only one ever , maybe ever .
#Text=Or we 'll head to the polls and together we 'll stop the left and win four more years in the White House .
#Text=We 're joined today by some incredible people , friends of mine , great , great people .
#Text=And I want to congratulate your governor because we had a spike and he knocked that spike out so fast .
#Text=I do n't know .
#Text=Are you sure you even had a spike ?
#Text=Doug Ducey , a great governor , great man , and a somebody that won by about 16 or 17 points .
#Text=That 's not so bad .
#Text=And I think you 're more popular today .
#Text=What a job you 've done .
#Text=Thank you very much , Doug .
#Text=A friend of mine and somebody who 's a great fighter pilot , and I had a lot of people tell me she could really wheel the Warthog , right ?
#Text=The Warthog .
#Text=She said , " I love that plane , " but she was a great , great fighter pilot , one of the best they were telling me .
#Text=This was a group and they knew a very well .
#Text=A lot of friends you have .
#Text=And specifically she said , " Could you extend that plane ?
#Text=That 's the best plane .
#Text=It never breaks down .
#Text=It just is a winner . "
#Text=But Martha McSally is an extraordinary person , and she 's fighting for us , and she 's helping us , and we have to bring her into the center .
#Text=Thank you ,
#Text=Martha .

#Text=And she 's running against a gentlemen who is , when you read what he 's done , when you read what he said about the second amendment and about all other things , you 're not going to want to vote for .
#Text=You 're not going to want to have them play with your second amendment .
#Text=I 'll tell you what .
#Text=If I were n't President , I do n't believe , Doug , you 'd have a second amendment right now .
#Text=I do n't think you 'd have .
#Text=The pressure that was put on to get rid of it , or to basically obliterate it , make it so it 's meaningless .
#Text=You will always have the right to bear arms .
#Text=You will always have that .
#Text=A few friends of mine who are warriors .
#Text=Paul Gosar .
#Text=Paul .
#Text=Where 's Paul ?
#Text=Paul , stand up .
#Text=Will you ?
#Text=Paul Gosar .
#Text=Thank you ,
#Text=Paul .
#Text=Appreciate .
#Text=Great job you 're doing .
#Text=These are warriors .
#Text=They really are .
#Text=When they went and they tried to make a play at your President , they had to get through the House .
#Text=What were we ?
#Text=197 and nothing .
#Text=That 's never happened before .
#Text=Everybody came together .
#Text=The Republicans came .
#Text=Other than Mitt Romney , one half a vote .
#Text=One half a brain .
#Text=Another friend of mine and incredible fighter , and somebody that loves his state , and I 'll tell you , the Freedom Caucus , right ?
#Text=And we have a man named Andy Biggs here .
#Text=He 's a fighter .
#Text=He 's a fighter .
#Text=And he loves our vets , and he loves our military , and you love our second amendment , right ?
#Text=And we 're not going to do anything with it .
#Text=They will destroy that second amendment .
#Text=Just remember I said it , but you 're not going to have to worry about it because it 's not going to happen .
#Text=A woman who really distinguished herself , she became a star .
#Text=She became a star overnight .
#Text=There was nobody tougher .
#Text=There was nobody smarter .
#Text=There was nobody better than Debbie Lesko .
#Text=Great job , Debbie .
#Text=Thank you .
#Text=We want her on our side .
#Text=Right fellas ?
#Text=We got to have her on our side .
#Text=Also , thanks to Arizona Republican party chairman , I knew this was going to happen .
#Text=I knew that she was going .
#Text=She never stops .
#Text=She never gives up .
#Text=Kelly Ward .
#Text=Kelly , thank you .
#Text=Thank you ,
#Text=Kelly .
#Text=Great job you 're doing .
#Text=Are we winning ?
#Text=Okay , good .
#Text=I think we are .
#Text=That 's what they say .
#Text=We better win .
#Text=If we do n't win , this country is in big trouble .
#Text=Big trouble .
#Text=Also a great friend of all of ours , former State Treasurer of Arizona , Jeff DeWitt .
#Text=Thank you Jeff .
#Text=And a man who did n't choke under pressure .
#Text=I do n't even know if he 's here .
#Text=I think he might be here .
#Text=He never choked .
#Text=He kicked for 11 years .
#Text=You know what that is ?
#Text=You ever see a golfer .
#Text=They miss a three footer .
#Text=They miss a three footer .
#Text=They ca n't take it back .
#Text=They choke , choke , choke .
#Text=Well , kickers are the same .
#Text=Right ?
#Text=NFL kickers .
#Text=This guy lasted 11 years .
#Text=He 's one of the best kickers ever .
#Text=NFL kicker , Jay Feely .
#Text=Where 's Jay ?
#Text=Where is Jay ?
#Text=He 's here someplace .
#Text=Where is he ?
#Text=Jay ?
#Text=What happened ?
#Text=You could n't get a good seat , Jay .
#Text=I remember the 61 yarder .
#Text=That was a heartbreaker .
#Text=Right ?
#Text=But the only thing is , I 'll bet you this man would stand , only stand , for our National Anthem .
#Text=That 's one thing .
#Text=That 's one thing I can tell you .
#Text=And if they do n't stand for our flag , if they do n't stand for our National Anthem , I turn off the game .
#Text=Other than that , I 'd like to watch , but I turn off the game .
#Text=And by the way , I thought they learned that lesson a little while ago .
#Text=I thought they learned that lesson two years ago , but maybe not , but they will .
#Text=They 'll learn it again .
#Text=This time it 'll go even faster .
#Text=For decades , Washington politicians like Biden allowed an endless supply of illegal foreign labor to decimate American jobs and wages .
#Text=Also , the crime was incredible what happened .
#Text=They allowed criminal gangs to menace , maim and terrorize innocent citizens .
#Text=They came in .
#Text=They would maim and terrorize , and we have done something with our border patrol .
#Text=And by the way , ICE , ICE is great .
#Text=ICE has taken out thousands and thousands of MS - 13 , and you do n't want the job .
#Text=There 's some tough people here .
#Text=None of you want the job .
#Text=It 's a tough job , but they like it , and they 're great Patriots , and they 've done a fantastic job .
#Text=They ceded control of the border to the most dangerous and ruthless cartels on earth .
#Text=This is what would happen .
#Text=They have ceded .
#Text=And what we 've done , did you ever notice the caravans ?
#Text=What happened ?
#Text=Debbie , there are no more caravans .
#Text=What happened ?
#Text=What happened to the caravans ?
#Text=They do n't come up anymore .
#Text=The caravans do n't come up .
#Text=You know , we were paying hundreds of millions of dollars to Honduras , Guatemala , El Salvador , hundreds of millions .
#Text=And I said , " Well , why are we doing that ? "
#Text=And they would n't take .
#Text=When we caught a murderer and we wanted to bring it back to one of those countries , they would n't take him .
#Text=And they would n't take him under the Obama administration .
#Text=So we got stuck with them because they 'd fly in .
#Text=They 'd say , " Do n't land your plane . "
#Text=And I said something very simple .
#Text=I said , " That 's okay .
#Text=We do n't have to do that .
#Text=We 're not going to pay you anymore .
#Text=We stopped payment . "
#Text=We stopped payment .
#Text=It 's amazing how that works , Doug .
#Text=Right ?
#Text=We stopped payment and they called .
#Text=They said , " We 'd love to take them .
#Text=We 'd be honored to take them . "
#Text=So we take them back by the thousands , by the thousands .
#Text=They let lethal poisonous drugs pour freely into our schools and our communities , but no more .
#Text=It 's not happening anymore .

#Text=The cruel and heartless portrayal of the American people ended the day I took the oath of office , and now that we have more than half of the wall built , and do you notice they do n't talk about the wall anymore .
#Text=They do n't talk .
#Text=Why do n't you talk ?
#Text=I went , " Look at all those people back there . "
#Text=That 's called fake news , fake news .
#Text=Look at them .
#Text=It 's the fake news .
#Text=They do n't talk about the wall anymore .
#Text=See , we won .
#Text=We got the wall .
#Text=It 's going to be up to 300 next week and it 's going to be finished very soon .
#Text=And as soon as we want , all of a sudden , they never talk about it .
#Text=But you know where I talk about it ?
#Text=Numbers .
#Text=The numbers are so good .
#Text=The numbers are so low .
#Text=We 've never had numbers like this because that big portion of wall already built , you do n't get through it .
#Text=You ca n't get through it .
#Text=You can climb Mount Everest , and you 're going to have an awful hard time getting over that sucker .
#Text=I stood up to the lobbyists .
#Text=Everybody fought us , the Democrats , everyone .
#Text=I fought the special interests .
#Text=I kept every single promise that I made , and now I 'm doing it with the drug companies .
#Text=I just created Favorite Nation .
#Text=So if a nation buys it for less and they buy it for a fraction of what we pay , the drug companies have to sell it to us for the same price .
#Text=And they 're spending so much .
#Text=They 're spending millions of dollars on advertising .
#Text=Anytime you see an ad from a drug company , and they 're rich , the farmer , it 's called Big Farmer , the number one lobbyist .
#Text=They spend millions and millions , hundreds of millions of dollars online .
#Text=Anytime you see , anytime at all , you see an ad by Big Farmer against me , you know your drug prices are coming down .
#Text=That 's what it is .
#Text=They 're not happy .
#Text=And we 're giving the rebate that creates tremendous wealth for the middle man , the rebate .
#Text=It 's going to the people now .
#Text=We 're bringing the rebate and it 's going to the people .
#Text=They are not happy .
#Text=I have a lot of people in that industry do not like me too much .
#Text=But you are going to get 50 .
#Text=You are going to get , and the Democrats would never do it , Biden would never do it because he does n't understand it , but they would never do it .
#Text=They would in a million years , they would n't do it .
#Text=It took a lot of guts to do it .
#Text=I had a lot of people , a lot of good politicians go , " Sir , I do n't think you should do it . "
#Text=I wonder why you 're saying that , but we did it .

#Text=We 're going to have drug prices reduced over a very short period of time , by not 2 % , and last year they went down a little bit , first time in 51 years that drug prices went down but a little bit , we 're going to have prices dropping 50 , 60 , and even 70 % .
#Text=Drugs .
#Text=About time .
#Text=And I 'm proud to say that they 've achieved the most secure border , our border patrol , in the history of the United States of America .
#Text=We now have the most secure border we 've ever had and it 's only going to get better .
#Text=And we want people to come in , but we want them to come in through merit , right ?
#Text=And we want people - … people to come in , but we want them to come in through merit , right ?
#Text=And we want people that are going to come in and are going to love for our country , not hate our country .
#Text=Here in Yuma , Arizona , we 've invested over $ 1.7 billion and poured 180,000 cubic yards , that 's a lot of concrete , to build 108 miles of powerful border wall .
#Text=I know who 's going to vote for me .
#Text=I do n't know though , I think I 'm going to win Yuma .
#Text=What do you think , Doug ?
#Text=I think , when I hear those numbers , when we hear those numbers , we 're winning .
#Text=We 're going to win Yuma big .
#Text=Now you see it and you see what 's going up and it 's an incredible structure , all capable , all wired up for cameras , for everything you can have .
#Text=Technology is incredible .
#Text=In total , I 've already completely planned for the final execution , we 're going to have , by the end of the year , everything that we said is going to be built .
#Text=We may actually build some more in some soft areas that we 've noticed over the last two years .
#Text=So we actually may put up some additional , but we will have it completed , everything we said , by the end of the year and nobody thought that was possible .
#Text=And we 've reduced illegal border crossings by 60 % since this time last year .
#Text=And if we keep going at the rate , it 'll be about 85 % in about two months .
#Text=So it 's a great honor .
#Text=And you know what ?
#Text=Your community is much safer , you see the difference , it 's a much safer place to be .
#Text=But more important than these numbers is the fact that we 've ended catch and release .
#Text=You know what catch and release is ?

#Text=These great men and women catch somebody , maybe a murderer , maybe a rapist , maybe a trafficker , they catch somebody , take his name , take his number and they release them into our country .
#Text=And they say , " Come back in four years , you have a trial . "
#Text=No more .
#Text=We take them out .
#Text=We bring them out .
#Text=And nobody said that was possible because I could n't have gotten it through the Democrats because they do n't like that .
#Text=So we have people coming in to this country , some great people , some really bad people too .
#Text=And I mean murders and I mean rapist , I mean really bad people and they do n't get in and they do n't get back .
#Text=When we bring them back to their country , could be Mexico also , they do n't come back .
#Text=Under the Obama Biden , I call it OBiden , Under the OBiden administration , our agents were ordered to ignore the law and release illegal aliens by the hundreds of thousands .
#Text=And by the way , Mark Morgan , where 's the great Mark Morgan ?
#Text=He 's around here someplace .
#Text=Mark Morgan has been so incredible , one of our executives , he said , " We never built the cages .
#Text=Those cages were built in 2014 by Obama . "
#Text=We never the cages , they were built by Obama and the fake news is constantly saying that I built cages for children .
#Text=I did n't build them .
#Text=They were built in 2014 .
#Text=There was a headline in Time magazine about the cage and somebody called in that built it .
#Text=They said , " He did n't build it , we built that for the Obama administration . "
#Text=But they do n't stop , they keep calling it , they say I built the cages .
#Text=You 'll hear it in one of the debates .
#Text=They 'll say , " You built cages president . "
#Text=I said , " No , I did n't build cages .
#Text=That was built by Obama . "
#Text=Under the Trump administration , if you cross our border illegally , you are quickly apprehended and swiftly returned back home .
#Text=We are proudly defending the job safety and security of the American people , which is what I promised to do .
#Text=Nobody told me it was going to be this hard .
#Text=Nobody told me I was going to have the Democrats go totally crazy .
#Text=This was like a life and death war .
#Text=You know why they do n't talk about it anymore ?
#Text=Because they know it 's bad politics , because they know having a wall , they ca n't win that one .
#Text=So they just say , " Let 's forget it ever happened . '
#Text=Because we won and they say , " Let 's forget . "
#Text=They do n't want to talk about it .
#Text=That includes the millions of incredible Hispanic Americans who follow our laws , uplift our community and protect our nation , in uniform .
#Text=Half of all border patrol agents are Hispanic Americans , I was just with them .
#Text=And today I salute each and every one of those true American heroes and that 's what they are .
#Text=And nobody understands the border better than Hispanics .
#Text=They know what 's good , what 's bad .
#Text=They do n't want bad people coming into our country , taking their jobs , taking their homes , causing crime .
#Text=Hispanic Americans are the people that are most in favor of what we 're doing on the border because they understand it .
#Text=They understand it better than anybody .

#Text=With the help of these patriots , we 've stopped the rampant asylum fraud , shut down the human smugglers and we 're finding the drug dealers , traffickers , predators , and we 're throwing them to hell in jail or sending them back home .
#Text=MS - 13 , for the first time that you 've ever seen this , MS - 13 is totally on the run .
#Text=Many of its leaders are right now behind bars and we 're deporting its members in record numbers we 've never reported .
#Text=I ca n't believe how many there are .
#Text=But if Biden wins , it will be a giant jail break for MS - 13 and vicious criminal gangs .
#Text=China wants him to win so badly .
#Text=Iran wants him to win so badly .
#Text=When we win , I 'll have a deal with the red within a month , watch , because they 're dying to make a deal .
#Text=But that last hope that Biden will win , they will own our country , China , they will own our country .
#Text=We made such a great deal .
#Text=Last week they had the largest order of corn in the history of our country , the largest single order .
#Text=Then they did it again .
#Text=You know why they 're doing that ?
#Text=Because they know I 'm angry , because they know I do n't care so much anymore .
#Text=We made a great trade deal , but I do n't care .
#Text=But it shows you how smart they are , Doug .
#Text=Another with normal brain power , they 'd say , " Well , I 'm not going to buy any more corn . "
#Text=That 's good .
#Text=And we 'll just decouple , thank you very much .
#Text=But they go the opposite .
#Text=They buy so much , good record numbers , soybeans record numbers .
#Text=Last week , biggest ever , 42 % of our farmers crop is now China , over the last little while .
#Text=You know why ?
#Text=Because they do n't want bad things to happen , that 's why .
#Text=So they 're very smart .
#Text=When I have every farmer in the country calling and saying , " Please do n't do anything . "
#Text=They 're very , very smart , but we can never forget what China did to this country and did to the world .
#Text=The historic achievements that I 've discussed today are only a slim fraction of the extraordinary accomplishment that we 've all done together in the last four years .
#Text=Here 's just a short list of our landmarks .
#Text=Really they are landmarks , true landmarks .
#Text=We instituted a national security travel ban on the world 's most dangerous regions , including jihadist regions , keeping terrorists and extremists out of our country .
#Text=Everyone said , " Oh , that 's so bad . "
#Text=Remember when they said , " Oh , that 's so bad . "
#Text=I do n't think it 's so bad at all .
#Text=We won the travel ban .
#Text=The fake news said we did n't because we lost in the lower court , we lost in the second court and we won in the Supreme court .
#Text=So they said we lost .
#Text=Can you believe it ?
#Text=They said we lost Debbie , because we lost the first two , but we won in the Supreme court , so they said , " They lost . "
